  "title": "Whipdashing",
  "description": "A Powerful Mobility Tool!",
  "body": "<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AmyMialeeMods/whipdashing/main/assets/ModFest_Singularity_Banner.png\" width=300 alt=\"Made for ModFest Singularity\">\n\nWhipdashing is a small mod which adds a new mobility tool, the Whipdash.  \nThis tool when equipped in your off-hand slot allows you to shoot a hook out which can be used to pull yourself towards heavy entities, or pull light entities towards yourself.  \nYou can also use the swap offhand key to have it pull you towards all entities, even projectiles.  \nThis mod was made as a part of ModFest: Singularity.  \n\n<table align=\"center\">\n    <tr>\n        <th><b>Join my Discord</b></th>\n        <th><b>Find the mod on Curseforge!</b></th>\n        <th><b>Find the mod on Modrinth!</b></th>\n        <th><b>Support me on Ko-fi!</b></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <th>\n            <a href=\"http://discord.amymialee.xyz\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/793182374410059887/924000460292104282/3437c10597c1526c3dbd98c737c2bcae.svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"Discord\">\n            </a>\n        </th>\n        <th>\n            <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/whipdashing\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/793182374410059887/923990008543711282/anvil.svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"Curseforge Eventually\">\n            </a>\n        </th>\n        <th>\n            <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/whipdashing\">\n                <img src=\"https://docs.modrinth.com/img/logo.svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n            </a>\n        </th>\n        <th>\n            <a href=\"http://kofi.amymialee.xyz\">\n                <img src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/kofi_stroke_cup.svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"Ko-fi\">\n            </a>\n        </th>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<b>Interested in hosting a server for any of my mods?</b>  \nBe sure to go with Bloom Host at:  \n<a href=\"http://bloom.amymialee.xyz\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h4556XW.gif\">\n</a>  \n<b>Buying a server using this link supports me directly!</b>",
